# Neofetch Test - Fixed Dimensions
# Tests neofetch with explicit width and height
# Content scrolls to fit within fixed viewport

Output examples/svgs/neofetch-fixed-dimensions.svg

Set Theme github-dark
Set Template macos
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Scroll false

Type "neofetch"

Sleep 500ms

Enter

Sleep 2s

Type "Fixed dimensions mode!"

Sleep 1s
